b5961faf1bf903fca0d92408f4b9a783e61b5c06e89c9318aa7f59c6ca98be922504909ae7cf59dd09e953378952f7af3335f3f71cb1ff9f5a8a8c8f7c729f6d  boost-1.77.patch
